                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Balto.</placeName>\n                <date>June 4th 1857</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir—</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I had this pleasure yester-<lb/>day in registered letter, with\n                enclosure $109.96/100,<lb/> in full of accot. Referring to my remarks<lb/> in same I\n                give below a copy of the statement<lb/> handed me by <persName>Dr.\n                    Guinsburg</persName></p>\n            <table cols=\"3\" rows=\"17\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>Mr Is. Leeser</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>Cr</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>For 2 doz. Readers @</cell>\n                    <cell>$4.__</cell>\n                    <cell>$8.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“ 2 “ <persName>Nath</persName> “ “</cell>\n                    <cell>2.40</cell>\n                    <cell>4.80</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“ 2 “ <persName>Pix.</persName> Quest. “</cell>\n                    <cell>4.80</cell>\n                    <cell>9.60</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“ 1 “ Catechisms “</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>6.—</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“ 1 “ Prayer Book</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\"> 2.—</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$30.40</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>Dr</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><persName>Mr Cohen</persName>, for him returned</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>18 Readers</cell>\n                    <cell>$6.—</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>18 <persName>Nath.</persName> Readers</cell>\n                    <cell>3.60</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>19 <persName>Pix.</persName> Quest.</cell>\n                    <cell>7.60</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>11 Catechisms</cell>\n                    <cell>5.50</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>1 Prayer Book</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">2.—</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$24.70</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>To Commo.10%</cell>\n                    <cell>—.57</cell>\n                    <cell>25.27</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>Sold</cell>\n                    <cell>5.13/100</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>I find some difference between his statement<lb/> as handed me, &amp; the number of\n                books handed me.</p>\n            "
                  },
